parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can result in serious injury or death.

the owner is unable to get a repair estimate or schedule a repair

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A fire in the heated seat can cause damage to the vehicle and potentially result in injury or death.
